    "titles": {
      "en": "Chapter on Departing Early to Mina Before the Day of Tarwiyah"
    },
    "verse_count": 4,
    "verse_start_index": 1407,
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications"
    ],
    "verses": [
      {
        "index": 1408,
        "local_index": 1,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2974 - "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/404",
              "text": "رُوِيَ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنْ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/44",
              "text": "إِسْحَاقَ بْنِ عَمَّارٍ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:116:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/116/1",
        "text": [
          " : قُلْتُ لِأَبِي اَلْحَسَنِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَتَعَجَّلُ اَلرَّجُلُ قَبْلَ اَلتَّرْوِيَةِ بِيَوْمٍ أَوْ يَوْمَيْنِ مِنْ أَجْلِ اَلزِّحَامِ وَ ضِغَاطِ اَلنَّاسِ فَقَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2974 - It was narrated from Ishaq ibn Ammar, who said:\nI said to Abu al-Hasan (as): \"Can a person leave for Mina a day or two before the Day of Tarwiyah to avoid the crowd and congestion?\"\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1409,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2975 - "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/213",
              "text": "و"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "َ قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:116:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/116/2",
        "text": [
          " فِي خَبَرٍ آخَرَ : «لاَ يَتَعَجَّلُ بِأَكْثَرَ مِنْ ثَلاَثَةِ أَيَّامٍ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2975 - In another narration, Imam (as) said:\n\"A person should not leave earlier than three days in advance.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1410,
        "local_index": 3,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2976 - وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "رَوَى جَمِيلُ بْنُ دَرَّاجٍ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنْ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "أَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:116:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/116/3",
        "text": [
          " : «عَلَى اَلْإِمَامِ أَنْ يُصَلِّيَ اَلظُّهْرَ بِمِنًى ثُمَّ يَبِيتَ بِهَا وَ يُصْبِحَ حَتَّى تَطْلُعَ اَلشَّمْسُ ثُمَّ يَخْرُجَ إِلَى عَرَفَاتٍ »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2976 - Jamil ibn Darraj narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"It is incumbent upon the Imam to pray the Zuhr prayer in Mina, spend the night there, and remain until sunrise. Then, he should depart for Arafat.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1411,
        "local_index": 4,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2977 - وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "سَأَلَ مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ مُسْلِمٍ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : هَلْ صَلَّى رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "آلِهِ اَلظُّهْرَ، بِمِنًى يَوْمَ اَلتَّرْوِيَةِ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:116:4",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/116/4",
        "text": [
          " «نَعَمْ وَ اَلْغَدَاةَ يَوْمَ عَرَفَةَ »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2977 - Muhammad ibn Muslim asked Abu Ja'far (as):\n\"Did the Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) pray the Zuhr prayer in Mina on the Day of Tarwiyah?\"\nImam (as) said: \"Yes, and also the Fajr prayer on the Day of Arafah.\""
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
